  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 9 (Spell Level 5)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 12</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 24 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 12 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 26</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> Mas, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You make an unarmed attack that is truly difficult to see, and can hit a creature up to 10 ft further than your melee reach. You gain a +4 bonus to the attack roll, and the attack deals 1d6 bonus damage per 2 levels (up to 10d6), which is not multiplied on critical hits. If hit, the target is knocked back 1d6 x 5 ft and becomes dazed for 1 round. A successful save negates both these secondary effects.<br><br>This attack is difficult to see and is harder to perform without the appropriate clothing, as with Kensoku: Iaiken.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The fifth step extends the range by another 10 ft.</p>\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
